      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Ready for a Project? This One's Got Potential! \u2014 Calling all DIY enthusiasts and mechanics! This vehicle is priced to move and offers a great opportunity for someone with the skills and vision to bring it back to life. We want to be fully transparent: this car is in poor condition and will require significant repairs before it's road-ready. Whether you're looking for a hands-on restoration project or a source of quality parts, this could be exactly what you've been searching for \u2014 at a price that reflects its current state honestly!",
