    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Still searching for a reliable, no-nonsense vehicle at a price that makes sense? This one's worth a look! It's in fair condition \u2014 it starts right up and drives dependably day in and day out, though it does show some visible wear and cosmetic imperfections that reflect its history on the road. Nothing here is hidden \u2014 what you see is what you get, and what you get is a functional, honest vehicle ready for its next owner. If you're after value over flash, this could be a smart pick!",
