    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Exceptional Mint-Condition Find \u2014 Truly Turn-Key! \ud83c\udf1f This vehicle has been lovingly maintained from day one and it shows \u2014 the paint gleams, the interior is spotless, and everything runs and functions exactly as it should. There are no hidden surprises here, just a genuinely well-kept car that's ready to impress the moment you take the wheel. Whether you're treating yourself or looking for a reliable daily driver that still feels special, this one delivers. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will speak for itself!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
