      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a reliable, well-maintained used car for the right buyer. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 you may notice a few small scratches or light scuffs, but nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The interior is clean and functional, with typical signs of regular use such as slight wear on high-contact surfaces. Mechanically, the car performs well and has been kept in good working order. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are operating as expected. This is a honest, everyday driver that will serve its next owner dependably without the premium cost of a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully before making a purchase decision. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 no major dents, rust, or body damage to report. The interior is clean and functional, with seats showing moderate wear but no tears or significant staining; all controls and features operate as expected. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues. The tires have reasonable tread remaining, and the brakes are in serviceable condition. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been maintained adequately and is ready for everyday driving. It is not a showroom-perfect car, but it is a genuinely good-condition used vehicle that should serve its next owner well.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and full transparency is important to us. The exterior shows considerable wear \u2014 expect visible rust, dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car requires attention \u2014 it has known issues and should be considered a project vehicle or a parts car rather than a daily driver without prior repairs. It may start and move under its own power, but reliability cannot be guaranteed. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the car's current state, and we strongly encourage any interested buyer to arrange a thorough inspection before purchasing. Best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a fixer-upper, or a buyer with a limited budget who understands the trade-offs involved.",
      "price": 7000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    }
